snippet.title: Exodus H - Announcement Trailer (EN)
snippet.description:
Take command of your own colonial ship. Ensure the survival of your inhabitants and try to find a new habitable planet. This is the goal of the the Exodus H Space Commanders.

Soon in Early Acces on Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/1616540/Exodus_H/
